<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Fluid Architecture · Responsive Design</title>

    <!-- ============================================================
    STYLES — Mobile-First, Fluid, Accessible
    ============================================================ -->
    <style>
        /* ---------- RESET & BASE ---------- */
        *,
        *::before,
        *::after {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        :root {
            --color-bg: #f8f6f3;
            --color-surface: #ffffff;
            --color-text: #1e1e2a;
            --color-muted: #5a5a6e;
            --color-accent: #c44536;
            --color-accent-light: #e8b4a8;
            --color-border: #d9d4ce;
            --color-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);

            --font-base: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            --font-mono: 'SF Mono', 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;

            /* Fluid spacing */
            --space-xs: clamp(0.25rem, 0.5vw, 0.5rem);
            --space-sm: clamp(0.5rem, 1vw, 1rem);
            --space-md: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 2rem);
            --space-lg: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 4rem);
            --space-xl: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 6rem);

            /* Fluid type — clamp(min, ideal, max) */
            --text-xs: clamp(0.7rem, 0.8vw + 0.4rem, 0.85rem);
            --text-sm: clamp(0.85rem, 1vw + 0.4rem, 1rem);
            --text-base: clamp(1rem, 1.2vw + 0.5rem, 1.2rem);
            --text-md: clamp(1.2rem, 1.6vw + 0.6rem, 1.6rem);
            --text-lg: clamp(1.6rem, 2.5vw + 0.8rem, 2.4rem);
            --text-xl: clamp(2.4rem, 4vw + 1rem, 4rem);
            --text-2xl: clamp(3.2rem, 5.5vw + 1.5rem, 5.6rem);

            --radius: 0.75rem;
            --radius-lg: 1.5rem;
            --transition: 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);

            /* Nav height for spacing */
            --nav-height: 4rem;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
            -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        }

        body {
            font-family: var(--font-base);
            font-size: var(--text-base);
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--color-text);
            background: var(--color-bg);
            padding: 0 var(--space-sm);
            padding-top: var(--nav-height);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        /* ---------- SKIP LINK (accessibility) ---------- */
        .skip-link {
            position: fixed;
            top: -999px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: var(--color-text);
            color: #fff;
            padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
            border-radius: 0 0 var(--radius) var(--radius);
            z-index: 9999;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: top 0.2s;
        }
        .skip-link:focus {
            top: 0;
        }

        /* ---------- CONTAINER ---------- */
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: var(--space-md) 0 var(--space-xl);
        }

        /* ---------- NAVIGATION (Popover API) ---------- */
        .site-nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            height: var(--nav-height);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0 var(--space-md);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px var(--color-shadow);
        }

        .site-nav .logo {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: var(--text-md);
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: var(--space-xs);
            color: var(--color-text);
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .site-nav .logo span {
            color: var(--color-accent);
        }

        /* Popover trigger button */
        .nav-toggle {
            background: none;
            border: none;
            padding: var(--space-xs);
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--color-text);
            transition: background var(--transition);
            min-width: 44px;
            min-height: 44px;
            /* touch target */;
        }
        .nav-toggle:hover,
        .nav-toggle:focus-visible {
            background: var(--color-border);
        }
        .nav-toggle svg {
            width: 28px;
            height: 28px;
            display: block;
            stroke: currentColor;
            fill: none;
            stroke-width: 2;
            stroke-linecap: round;
            stroke-linejoin: round;
        }

        /* Popover element */
        .nav-popover {
            position: fixed;
            top: var(--nav-height);
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.97);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space-md);
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
            margin: 0;
            overflow-y: auto;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            pointer-events: none;
            /* hidden by default */;
        }
        .nav-popover:popover-open {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
            pointer-events: auto;
        }

        .nav-popover ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: var(--space-md);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .nav-popover ul li a {
            display: block;
            padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
            font-size: var(--text-lg);
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--color-text);
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            transition: background var(--transition), color var(--transition);
            min-height: 52px;
            /* accessible touch */;
        }
        .nav-popover ul li a:hover,
        .nav-popover ul li a:focus-visible {
            background: var(--color-accent-light);
            color: var(--color-accent);
        }

        /* Close button inside popover */
        .nav-close {
            display: block;
            margin: var(--space-md) auto 0;
            padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-lg);
            background: var(--color-border);
            border: none;
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            font-size: var(--text-sm);
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: var(--color-text);
            transition: background var(--transition);
            min-height: 44px;
            min-width: 44px;
        }
        .nav-close:hover,
        .nav-close:focus-visible {
            background: var(--color-accent);
            color: #fff;
        }

        /* ---------- HERO / HEADER ---------- */
        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-sm) var(--space-lg);
            background: var(--color-surface);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px var(--color-shadow);
            margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
            border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: var(--text-2xl);
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
        }
        .hero h1 span {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-accent), #a83226);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: var(--text-md);
            color: var(--color-muted);
            max-width: 640px;
            margin: 0 auto var(--space-md);
        }
        .hero .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--color-accent-light);
            color: var(--color-accent);
            padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-md);
            border-radius: 100px;
            font-size: var(--text-xs);
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        }

        /* ---------- GRID LAYOUT (Macro) ---------- */
        .grid-layout {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: var(--space-lg);
            margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
        }

        /* ---------- CARD (used for sections) ---------- */
        .card {
            background: var(--color-surface);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            padding: var(--space-lg);
            border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px var(--color-shadow);
            transition: box-shadow var(--transition);
        }
        .card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07);
        }

        .card h2 {
            font-size: var(--text-lg);
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: var(--space-xs);
        }
        .card h2 .emoji {
            font-size: var(--text-md);
        }
        .card p,
        .card li {
            color: var(--color-muted);
            font-size: var(--text-sm);
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .card ul,
        .card ol {
            padding-left: var(--space-md);
            margin: var(--space-sm) 0;
        }
        .card li {
            margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
        }

        /* ---------- FLEXBOX COMPONENTS (Micro) ---------- */
        .flex-row {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: var(--space-md);
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: var(--space-md);
        }
        .flex-row .btn {
            flex: 0 1 auto;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: var(--space-xs);
            padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-lg);
            background: var(--color-text);
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 100px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: var(--text-sm);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background var(--transition), transform var(--transition);
            text-decoration: none;
            min-height: 44px;
            min-width: 44px;
            /* accessible */;
        }
        .btn:hover,
        .btn:focus-visible {
            background: var(--color-accent);
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }
        .btn-outline {
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--color-text);
            border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
        }
        .btn-outline:hover,
        .btn-outline:focus-visible {
            background: var(--color-border);
            color: var(--color-text);
            border-color: var(--color-text);
        }

        /* ---------- FEATURE GRID (inside card) ---------- */
        .feature-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: var(--space-md);
            margin-top: var(--space-md);
        }
        .feature-item {
            background: var(--color-bg);
            padding: var(--space-md);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
        }
        .feature-item h3 {
            font-size: var(--text-base);
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
        }
        .feature-item p {
            font-size: var(--text-sm);
            color: var(--color-muted);
            margin: 0;
        }
        .feature-item code {
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: var(--text-xs);
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem;
            border-radius: 0.25rem;
            color: var(--color-accent);
        }

        /* ---------- FLUID TYPOGRAPHY DEMO ---------- */
        .type-demo {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: var(--space-sm);
            margin-top: var(--space-sm);
        }
        .type-demo .sample {
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--color-border);
            padding-bottom: var(--space-xs);
        }
        .type-demo .sample-1 {
            font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
        }
        .type-demo .sample-2 {
            font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
        }
        .type-demo .sample-3 {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 5rem);
        }
        .type-demo .note {
            font-size: var(--text-xs);
            color: var(--color-muted);
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
        }

        /* ---------- ACCESSIBILITY BADGE ---------- */
        .a11y-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: var(--space-xs);
            background: #e2f0e6;
            color: #1e6b3b;
            padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-md);
            border-radius: 100px;
            font-size: var(--text-xs);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* ---------- FOOTER ---------- */
        .site-footer {
            margin-top: var(--space-xl);
            padding: var(--space-lg) 0;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
            text-align: center;
            font-size: var(--text-sm);
            color: var(--color-muted);
        }
        .site-footer a {
            color: var(--color-text);
            text-decoration: underline;
            text-underline-offset: 2px;
        }
        .site-footer a:hover {
            color: var(--color-accent);
        }

        /* ---------- RESPONSIVE: TABLET & UP ---------- */
        @media (min-width: 640px) {
            .grid-layout {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }
            .feature-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }
            .nav-popover ul {
                flex-direction: row;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                justify-content: center;
                gap: var(--space-sm);
            }
            .nav-popover ul li a {
                font-size: var(--text-base);
                padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-lg);
                min-height: 44px;
            }
            .nav-close {
                display: none;
                /* close button not needed on desktop */;
            }
        }

        @media (min-width: 900px) {
            .grid-layout {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            }
            .feature-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            }
            .nav-popover {
                position: static;
                background: transparent;
                backdrop-filter: none;
                -webkit-backdrop-filter: none;
                padding: 0;
                border: none;
                opacity: 1;
                transform: none;
                pointer-events: auto;
                overflow: visible;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                width: auto;
                height: auto;
                top: auto;
                left: auto;
                right: auto;
                bottom: auto;
            }
            .nav-popover ul {
                flex-direction: row;
                gap: var(--space-xs);
                margin: 0;
            }
            .nav-popover ul li a {
                font-size: var(--text-sm);
                padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-md);
                color: var(--color-muted);
                border-radius: 100px;
                min-height: 44px;
            }
            .nav-popover ul li a:hover,
            .nav-popover ul li a:focus-visible {
                background: var(--color-accent-light);
                color: var(--color-accent);
            }
            .nav-toggle {
                display: none;
            }
            .nav-close {
                display: none;
            }
        }

        /* ---------- ZOOM SAFE (accessibility) ---------- */
        @media screen and (max-width: 500px) {
            body {
                padding-left: var(--space-xs);
                padding-right: var(--space-xs);
            }
            .card {
                padding: var(--space-md);
            }
            .hero {
                padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space-sm);
            }
        }

        /* ---------- REDUCED MOTION ---------- */
        @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
            *,
            *::before,
            *::after {
                animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
                transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
                scroll-behavior: auto !important;
            }
        }

        /* ---------- PRINT ---------- */
        @media print {
            .site-nav {
                position: static;
                background: #fff;
                backdrop-filter: none;
                -webkit-backdrop-filter: none;
                box-shadow: none;
                border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
            }
            .nav-popover {
                position: static;
                opacity: 1;
                transform: none;
                pointer-events: auto;
                background: transparent;
                padding: 0;
                border: none;
            }
            .nav-toggle,
            .nav-close {
                display: none !important;
            }
            .card {
                box-shadow: none;
                border: 1px solid #ccc;
                break-inside: avoid;
            }
            .hero {
                box-shadow: none;
                border: 1px solid #ccc;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- ====== SKIP LINK ====== -->
    <a class="skip-link" href="#main">Skip to main content</a>

    <!-- ====== NAVIGATION (Popover API) ====== -->
    <nav class="site-nav" aria-label="Main navigation">
        <a href="#" class="logo" aria-label="Home">
            <span>◈</span> Fluid<span>.</span>
        </a>

        <!-- Popover trigger -->
        <button class="nav-toggle" popovertarget="nav-popover" aria-label="Open menu" aria-expanded="false">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <line x1="4" y1="7" x2="20" y2="7" />
                <line x1="4" y1="12" x2="20" y2="12" />
                <line x1="4" y1="17" x2="20" y2="17" />
            </svg>
        </button>

        <!-- Popover menu -->
        <div id="nav-popover" class="nav-popover" popover role="menu" aria-label="Main menu">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#layout" role="menuitem">Layout</a></li>
                <li><a href="#typography" role="menuitem">Typography</a></li>
                <li><a href="#components" role="menuitem">Components</a></li>
                <li><a href="#accessibility" role="menuitem">A11y</a></li>
                <li><a href="#future" role="menuitem">Future</a></li>
            </ul>
            <button class="nav-close" popovertarget="nav-popover" aria-label="Close menu">✕ Close</button>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- ====== MAIN CONTENT ====== -->
    <main id="main" class="container">

        <!-- HERO -->
        <header class="hero">
            <h1>Content is <span>Like Water</span></h1>
            <p>Building responsive architectures from the content out — fluid, accessible, and future-proof.</p>
            <div class="badge">✦ 62.73% Mobile Traffic</div>
            <div style="margin-top: var(--space-md); display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--space-sm); justify-content: center;">
                <span class="a11y-badge">♿ WCAG Compliant</span>
                <span class="a11y-badge" style="background:#e6e2f0;color:#4a3f6b;">↕ 500% Zoom</span>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- ====== GRID LAYOUT (Macro) ====== -->
        <section class="grid-layout" id="layout">

            <!-- CARD 1: Meta Viewport -->
            <article class="card">
                <h2><span class="emoji">📱</span> The Key to the Kingdom</h2>
                <p><code>&lt;meta name=&quot;viewport&quot; content=&quot;width=device-width, initial-scale=1&quot;&gt;</code></p>
                <div style="margin-top: var(--space-sm); display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--space-sm); font-size: var(--text-sm);">
                    <div style="background: #f1e9e7; padding: var(--space-sm); border-radius: var(--radius);">
                        <strong style="color:#b33a2a;">Without Tag</strong>
                        <p style="margin:0; font-size:var(--text-xs);">800px · fixed width — the lie</p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background: #e2f0e6; padding: var(--space-sm); border-radius: var(--radius);">
                        <strong style="color:#1e6b3b;">With Tag</strong>
                        <p style="margin:0; font-size:var(--text-xs);">Seamless integration — the truth</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p style="margin-top: var(--space-sm); font-size: var(--text-xs);">
                    <strong>✓</strong> width=device-width · <strong>✓</strong> initial-scale=1
                </p>
            </article>

            <!-- CARD 2: Mobile-First -->
            <article class="card">
                <h2><span class="emoji">📈</span> Mobile-First Strategy</h2>
                <p>Complexity increases with space.</p>
                <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
                    <li style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-sm); padding: var(--space-xs) 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
                        <span style="font-size:var(--text-xs); background:var(--color-text); color:#fff; padding:0.1rem 0.6rem; border-radius:100px;">1</span>
                        <span><strong>Mobile Core</strong> — Base CSS</span>
                    </li>
                    <li style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-sm); padding: var(--space-xs) 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
                        <span style="font-size:var(--text-xs); background:var(--color-text); color:#fff; padding:0.1rem 0.6rem; border-radius:100px;">2</span>
                        <span><strong>Tablet</strong> — Layout enhancements</span>
                    </li>
                    <li style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-sm); padding: var(--space-xs) 0;">
                        <span style="font-size:var(--text-xs); background:var(--color-text); color:#fff; padding:0.1rem 0.6rem; border-radius:100px;">3</span>
                        <span><strong>Desktop</strong> — High-res assets &amp; full layout</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p style="font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-muted); margin-top: var(--space-xs);">⬆ Complexity Increases with Space</p>
            </article>

            <!-- CARD 3: Breakpoints -->
            <article class="card">
                <h2><span class="emoji">🌉</span> Breakpoints are Bridges</h2>
                <p>Design for content breakage, not device models.</p>
                <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--space-xs); margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
                    <span style="background:var(--color-border); padding:0.2rem 0.8rem; border-radius:100px; font-size:var(--text-xs); font-weight:600;">480px</span>
                    <span style="background:var(--color-border); padding:0.2rem 0.8rem; border-radius:100px; font-size:var(--text-xs); font-weight:600;">768px</span>
                    <span style="background:var(--color-border); padding:0.2rem 0.8rem; border-radius:100px; font-size:var(--text-xs); font-weight:600;">1024px</span>
                    <span style="background:var(--color-accent-light); color:var(--color-accent); padding:0.2rem 0.8rem; border-radius:100px; font-size:var(--text-xs); font-weight:600;">+ content-driven</span>
                </div>
                <p style="font-size: var(--text-xs); margin-top: var(--space-sm);">— bridges, not fences —</p>
            </article>
        </section>

        <!-- ====== FLEXBOX + GRID HARMONY ====== -->
